Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:30.92,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 如果\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey! If?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.62,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,没有如果 小子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There is no if about this, laddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.87,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,现在 她挨了兰德尔几拳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now, she took a few blows at the hands of Randall
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.21,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还能保持沉默 这已经超出\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and kept silent, which is a fair sight more
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.13,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我都普通女性的期望了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}than I 'd expect of any ordinary woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.41,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,但你知道兰德尔的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But you know Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.88,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你知道他能力\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know what he's capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:44.63,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,如果她再落入他的手里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you think'll happen to her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.13,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你觉得她会有怎样的下场\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}if she falls into his hands again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.42,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,因此你娶我是为了保护我的安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you married me to keep me safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.61,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:01.38,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这是主要原因\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你有我的姓氏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You have my name,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.21,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我的宗族\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}my clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:15.04,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我的家庭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.25,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,并且 如果必要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And, if necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.87,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还有我身体的保护\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the protection of my body as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.10,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,和我谈谈你的家族\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Tell me about your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.97,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,要追溯到第几代\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How many generations back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.00,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你父母亲的就可以了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your parents will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.39,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:19.64,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我的父亲姓弗雷泽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My father was a Fraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:23.15,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,当然 了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:27.35,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,是现任领主同父异母的弟弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A younger half-brother to the present master...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.52,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还有科勒姆和杜格尔 我的母亲是艾琳 麦肯齐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Colum and Dougal... my mother was Aileen Mackenzie,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.60,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,科勒姆和杜格尔的姐姐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the elder sister of Colum and Dougal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,科勒姆希望我母亲嫁给马尔科姆 格兰特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Colum wished my mother to marry Malcolm Grant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.83,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我的阿姨珍妮特去世了 跟我母亲一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My aunt Janet is dead, like my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.49,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,但我的阿姨伊俄卡斯忒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but my aunt Jocasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.61,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我的父亲一直看着我长大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I had my father see me grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.00,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我对此总是心存感谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was always grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.70,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,很显然 这是在转移话题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was a distraction, to be sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:48.04,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,但我们两个都觉得很愉快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but a welcome one for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:49.92,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,当他告诉我他的家族历史时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When he told me his family history,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.12,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我也告诉了他我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I reciprocated in kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.88,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我们共度接下来的几小时\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and we each spent the next several hours
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:57.71,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,喝酒 聊天 还有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}drinking and talking and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.65,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,第一次 大概的了解彼此\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}generally getting to know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.28,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,新的配偶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}our new spouses for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:05.60,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,和女孩在一起的第一晚 每个人等着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First evening with the girl, everyone waited
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.39,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,想看她是否会接受她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to see would she take him or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.36,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他很迷人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He was charming,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.23,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,一个天生的讲故事的人 像大多数苏格兰人一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a born storyteller, like most Scots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:15.23,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,她让马尔科姆 格兰特离开\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She told Malcolm Grant off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.32,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,最终他只好回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And he headed home as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:21.04,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,随着时间的流逝 我开始放松了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}As the hours passed, I began to relax
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.04,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,最终开始享受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and eventually to enjoy myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.46,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你母亲呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.58,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,她和我父亲就在300个族人眼皮子底下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She and my father slipped out of the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:32.33,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,偷偷地从城堡溜走了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}right under the noses of 300 clansmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.08,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我的父亲很爱说那个故事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And my father loved telling that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.59,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我跟你说了滚开 蠢货\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I told you to stand back, ye coof ye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.26,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我可不要在外头徘徊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wasn't gonna ponce around outside the door, was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,等着他们回答\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Waiting for them to answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.27,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我们来只是喝杯茶什么的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}like we were just coming by for a nice cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:52.02,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你究竟在干什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And just what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.94,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,杜格尔派我们来看看你们是不是 呃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dougal sent us up to see if ye'd, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:57.41,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-你懂吗 -现在 谁才是蠢货\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- y'ken? - Now, who's the coof?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.69,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他们还穿着衣服呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They've still got their clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.29,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-出去 -你穿着衣服也可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Get out. - You can still do it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.28,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-继续做 -我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- with your clothes on. - I know that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,但新婚夜可不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but not on your wedding night!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.20,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我只是希望能\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I was just hoping to get
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.16,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,偷看下她的胸部\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}a wee keek at her breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.29,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他们是你的亲戚吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're related to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.01,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,只有鲁柏特才是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rupert only.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.59,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,远房表兄弟\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Distant cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:30.89,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,太晚了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's getting rather late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.53,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,也许我们该上床了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Perhaps we should go to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.65,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,上床\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.15,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还是睡觉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}or to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.79,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你说呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.80,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 你穿着束腹\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Either way you're... not likely to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.22,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,没法睡觉的 所以我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in your corset, so I 'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.50,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我来帮你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll help you with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.89,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,解开带子吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the laces and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.87,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,先脱裙子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Skirts first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.62,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:20.73,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,该我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.85,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你在哪学到那样子接吻的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where did you learn to kiss like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.25,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我只说过我是个处男\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I said I was a virgin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,可没说是个修道士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}not a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:09.49,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,如果我需要指导 我会问的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I need guidance... I'll ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.17,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:38.30,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,吉米 你压痛我了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jamie, you're crushing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.17,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,跟你想象的一样吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So was it like you thought it would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:51.79,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,差不多\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.63,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.47,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不 算了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}no, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:03.86,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,什么 告诉我呗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:06.52,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,跟你说了你会笑我的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You'll laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.36,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我保证不会笑你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Promise, I won't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.24,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道你喜欢面对面的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didna realize you did it face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.29,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为你喜欢背入式的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I thought you must do it the back way,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:28.75,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你知道 像马一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you know, like... like horses, ye ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.33,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:36.50,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 我说过我不会笑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know, I promised I wouldn't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.42,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我想问你个问题\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.81,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,尽管问\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.89,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.18,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.35,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.82,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,看来穆塔夫说得对\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murtagh was right about that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,穆塔夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Murtagh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:59.86,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他说一般女人都不会喜欢这种姿势\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He said women generally do not care for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.61,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他和鲁伯特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, he and Rupert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.45,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还有内德\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And Ned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:08.79,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他们为昨晚的事提了很多主意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They offered a lot of advice on the subject last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.26,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢 杰米\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I did like it, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.18,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,事情就是这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}There it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:43.14,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我变成了重婚者和荡妇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not only was I a bigamist and an adulteress,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,而我居然还很享受\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I 'd enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我去拿点东西吃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I need to get some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:51.15,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,克莱尔 等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Claire, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:57.45,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.82,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 小妞 如果你现在还能跑能跳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, lass, if you're still able to walk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:02.37,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,说明杰米昨晚没有尽到责任哦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Jamie isna doing his duty by ye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:04.54,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,如果她让你精疲力尽了 杰米\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If she's worn out already, Jamie,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.25,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我会很乐意代替你的位置的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll be more than happy to fill your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:12.08,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,住嘴 让我们清静点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bit of a curse and give us peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.67,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你最好回去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Better go back inside, Sassenach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.14,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他们在尽兴之前是不会停止取笑我们的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Until they've had their fun, they'll no leave us alone.
