Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.10,0:28:47.10,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,对外公示\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}announced three times on three consecutive...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.18,0:28:49.52,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,听着 你个懒鬼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look, you dozy smout!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.19,0:28:56.44,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你不是在法律之下 但在恩典之下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Yer not under the law... but under grace."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.49,0:28:59.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,出自 罗马书 第6章第14节\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Romans 6:14.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.66,0:29:04.20,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,如果你是从拜恩神父那里学教义问答书\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you'd learned your catechism from father Bain,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.28,0:29:05.58,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,那么你也该学学 圣经诗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you'd ken your bible verses too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.62,0:29:09.40,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,要注意你自身和自身的教义\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Take heed unto thyself, and unto the doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.59,0:29:13.01,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,持之以恒 才能解救你自身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Continue in them: for in doing this thou shalt both
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.09,0:29:16.21,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,以及那些听从于你的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}save thyself and them that hear thee."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.29,0:29:18.63,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,出自 提摩太前书 第4章\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}1 Timothy, chapter 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.71,0:29:20.43,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,第16节\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}verse 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.47,0:29:23.10,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不要忘记款待陌生人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Be not forgetful to entertain strangers,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.13,0:29:26.35,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,因为有人因此在不经意间款待了天使\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for thereby some have entertained angels unawares."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.44,0:29:29.06,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不要被各式各样的怪异教义引入歧途\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Be not carried about with divers and strange doctrines."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.14,0:29:31.03,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-你把诗句弄混了 -这都来自 希伯来书\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You're mixing up the verses. - It's all Hebrews.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.11,0:29:32.98,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-你不能这么做 -够了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Well, ye canna do that. - Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.15,0:29:37.48,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这里比女巫的乳头还冷\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's colder than a witch's tit in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.57,0:29:39.32,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不管有没有结婚预告\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ye'll perform the ceremony tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.40,0:29:41.65,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你明天都有主持仪式 否则你就主持你自己的最后仪式吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}banns or no, or you'll be performing yo last rite.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.70,0:29:43.62,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,来啊 杀了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go ahead, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.66,0:29:46.99,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,就算我葬身火海\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Even if I burn in the fiery pit,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.08,0:29:49.33,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,都好过在这痛苦的冰窖中\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}it'd be better than spending one more Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.41,0:29:51.13,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,再度过一周\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in this miserable freezing box.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.33,0:29:59.00,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,给你单独准备间房间怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}How would you like your own proper windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.05,0:30:02.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,杜戈尔说那个小个子立马就问\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dougal said that the wee man barely skipped a beat
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.64,0:30:04.31,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我们什么时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}before asking what time we would like
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.34,0:30:06.51,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,要举行仪式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the ceremony to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.56,0:30:09.15,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,教堂和金钱 有些东西永远都不会变\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Church and money: some things don't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.18,0:30:10.51,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-嗯 -给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Mm. - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.66,0:30:19.49,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你的下一个条件是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What was your next condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.52,0:30:21.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,如果你让我比完这场比赛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If ye'd have let me finish the game,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.24,0:30:22.61,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我就能替我们赢回一枚戒指\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I woulda won us a proper ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.69,0:30:24.41,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 这就是杰米要的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, this is what Jamie wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.50,0:30:29.03,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,既然他决定结婚 那这就是他应得的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and since it's his wedding, this is what he'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.08,0:30:31.70,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-日安 -日安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Good day to you. - Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.79,0:30:33.54,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你是铁匠吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Are you the blacksmith?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.59,0:30:37.17,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他当然是铁匠  你个蠢货\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Of course he's the blacksmith, ye great gob.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.01,0:30:41.01,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我们想要一个戒指\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We want a ring made.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:43.63,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-一个婚戒 -给一个女孩的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- A wedding ring. - For a lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.72,0:30:46.13,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,-你能打吗 -一个婚戒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Can you do it? - A wedding ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.22,0:30:47.97,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,应该可以\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.05,0:30:49.32,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我在后面有一些银\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I've got some silver in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.35,0:30:51.27,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不 用这个做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. Make it from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.69,0:30:55.81,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这是把很好的钥匙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's a perfectly good key.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.89,0:30:56.81,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,熔了它有点可惜\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It would be a shame to melt that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.90,0:30:58.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,哦 别全熔了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, dinna melt it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.61,0:31:01.78,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,新郎希望你可以留着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The groom wants you to keep the mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.87,0:31:05.45,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,插入锁的那部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the part that goes into the lock
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.54,0:31:08.99,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还有 那个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and... the...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.07,0:31:10.57,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,末尾的部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}part on the other end.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.63,0:31:12.96,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,钥匙齿和钥匙把\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the blade and the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.04,0:31:17.25,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 对对 钥匙齿和钥匙把 - 你不也不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Aye, the blade and the bow. - You didna ken that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.30,0:31:18.97,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.05,0:31:20.08,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,可以做\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.14,0:31:22.64,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,下星期来拿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.72,0:31:25.06,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 今天就要 - 那要额外收费\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Today. - It'll cost ye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.06,0:31:28.06,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,把钱给他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Give him the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.90,0:31:38.94,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.11,0:31:41.61,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你说你会付一半的钱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ye said ye'd pay half.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.69,0:31:44.07,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你要没把我从赌局上拉出来 我肯定会付的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I would have, had you not taken me out of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.11,0:31:45.61,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,钥匙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}A key.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.25,0:31:53.33,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,开什么的钥匙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Key to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.42,0:31:56.12,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.17,0:31:59.42,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我在我毛皮袋里挖到的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was just something I had in my sporran.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.71,0:32:04.13,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你第三个条件是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What was your third condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.27,0:32:08.48,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我留给奈德了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I left that to Ned.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.77,0:32:10.72,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这件怎么样 喜欢吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about this one? Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.80,0:32:12.97,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,小姐 表这样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}M-mistress, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.05,0:32:15.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我是来这买衣服的 不是女人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm here to find a dress, not a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.27,0:32:16.47,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.52,0:32:18.06,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这件的颜色我最喜欢了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This one's my favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.14,0:32:19.64,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢吗 - 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Do you like it? - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.69,0:32:22.06,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 看看背面 - 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Look what it does at the back. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.15,0:32:23.36,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 有蕾丝边哦 - 嗯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It laces up. - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.45,0:32:26.57,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 那你喜欢这件吗 - 额\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Do you want this one, then? - Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.65,0:32:31.37,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还有你喜欢衣服里面的这个吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Wouldn't you like to take me out of this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.37,0:32:36.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,新娘不是个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The... the bride isn't a...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.83,0:32:39.25,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 不检点的女人 - 对 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- a woman of loose morals? - Aye, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.33,0:32:43.30,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,她 她可不能在婚礼上穿这个\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's a... she can't be wearing that on her wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.33,0:32:46.00,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,那么你可不应该在妓院\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then maybe ye shouldn't be shopping for a dress
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.09,0:32:47.72,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,买婚纱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}at a whorehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.81,0:32:51.18,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我有适合你的婚纱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have something might suit ye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.23,0:32:53.06,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,走开 快\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get back, back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.14,0:32:54.60,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不然我可要拧你们耳朵了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Or I 'll clout your ears for ye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:59.60,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这件可是来自一位我们都熟知的贵族的恩赐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Courtesy of a certain lord with whom we are familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.68,0:33:02.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他在伦敦为他女人买的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}His lordship bought it in London for his lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.27,0:33:04.61,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,在回家的路上 在斯特林一家酒馆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}On his way home, he lost the rest of his money
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.69,0:33:06.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,丢了所有的钱\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}at the tables in Stirling,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.27,0:33:07.69,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,所以当他来光顾我们这儿的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so when he came by us for his usual visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.78,0:33:12.20,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,欲火熊熊 却囊中羞涩\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}he was long on desire but a wee bit short on clink.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.25,0:33:14.70,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他想用这件婚纱来交易 我接受了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He proposed a trade and I accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.78,0:33:17.03,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,从来没穿过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Never been worn.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.12,0:33:19.59,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,等候一位绅士来取走它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Was waiting for a gentleman to visit before putting it on,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.67,0:33:22.37,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不过我觉得还是不拿出来为好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I suppose it's best I never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:25.38,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,没有女人愿意在婚礼上\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No lass should wear another woman's dress
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.41,0:33:26.13,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,穿别的女人的衣服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on her wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.21,0:33:29.26,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 这件非常合适\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, that'll do nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.35,0:33:33.55,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,收你一先令\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Cost ye a schilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.64,0:33:37.14,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧好吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fine, fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.73,0:33:43.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你买完就要走吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, must you run off straight away?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.65,0:33:47.06,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,姑娘们还需要几分钟时间来包一下衣服\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It will take the girls a few minutes to wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.15,0:33:49.28,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,以防天气骤变\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Protect it from the whether, ye ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.37,0:33:52.24,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以为您提供一些娱乐活动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Perhaps we could offer ye some entertainment
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.29,0:33:54.24,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,在你等待的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.38,0:34:02.46,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 来嘛 - 慢慢来嘛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Come on. - Now, just slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.55,0:34:05.25,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,别这么急\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.33,0:34:06.38,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.42,0:34:07.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你肯定是胡编乱造的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now you're just making things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.75,0:34:12.42,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,没有 我把奈德的话一模一样说给你听了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, I-I told it to you exactly as Ned told it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.34,0:34:16.31,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,当时他笑得像只摇尾巴狗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Grinning like a dog with twa tails
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.39,0:34:19.85,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,满脸容光焕发\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and beaming red the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.93,0:34:22.15,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你看到婚礼上那个妓女了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did ye not see the strumpet at the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.23,0:34:24.27,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 噢 就是那个妓女啊 - 对的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Oh, so that's who that was. - Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.32,0:34:26.32,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我当时都不知道原来还有这档子事儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I had no idea that all that was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.40,0:34:28.82,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.91,0:34:31.78,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你还没告诉我你都做什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ye've not told me what you were doing all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.62,0:34:39.67,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.79,0:34:44.92,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 站起来 小姑娘\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, on your feet, lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.96,0:34:47.34,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你可不会想烂醉如泥地\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You hardly wanna get married
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.43,0:34:49.38,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,去结婚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}looking like a melted candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.46,0:34:51.63,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,烂醉如啥\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Like a what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.71,0:34:53.63,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,哦天啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.72,0:34:56.72,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,那么 你一点也记不起婚礼上的事儿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So, do ye no remember anything of your own wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.80,0:35:00.94,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 事实上 我记得一点 - 啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- As a matter of fact, I do. - Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.97,0:35:04.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,记得我那天宿醉未醒这件事儿 至少\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I did have a monstrous hangover, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.28,0:35:06.64,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.73,0:35:10.73,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我却记得每个一时刻 每一分每一秒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I remember every moment, every second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.40,0:35:15.70,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我永远忘不了走出教堂的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll never forget when I came out of the church
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.79,0:35:20.24,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,第一眼看到你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and saw you for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.33,0:35:23.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,感觉好像我走出门阴云密布\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was as if I stepped outside on a cloudy day
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.54,0:35:26.46,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,突然一下子就云开见日了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and suddenly the sun came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.89,0:36:27.89,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我永远效劳于你 女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Your servant, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.82,0:36:43.49,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我不能嫁给你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.57,0:36:45.54,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我连你叫什么都不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't even know your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.88,0:36:51.55,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我叫弗雷泽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's Fraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.60,0:36:54.10,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 亚历山大\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James Alexander
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.39,0:36:58.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,马尔科姆 麦肯齐 弗雷泽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Malcolm Mackenzie Fraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.59,0:37:03.68,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,克莱尔 伊丽莎白 毕彻姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Claire Elizabeth Beauchamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.52,0:37:18.16,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你们俩如果聊完了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, if you two are quite finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.24,0:37:19.66,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,那我们继续吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}let's get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.36,0:37:26.17,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你一点也不记得了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So you don't remember any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.25,0:37:30.12,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,还记得一点点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Not all of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.20,0:37:32.87,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,有件事儿还记得非常清晰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but some things are very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.68,0:38:01.62,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我 詹姆斯 亚历山大 马尔科姆 麦肯齐 弗雷泽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I, James Alexander Malcolm Mackenzie Fraser
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.69,0:38:04.54,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,愿意娶 克莱尔 伊丽莎白 毕彻姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}take, thee, Claire Elizabeth Beauchamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.62,0:38:06.54,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,作为我的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to be my wedded wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.62,0:38:09.83,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,从今开始 执子之手 与子偕老\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to have and to hold from this day forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.88,0:38:13.50,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,同甘共苦 生死相依\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for better or for worse, in sickness and in health...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.55,0:38:15.58,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,至死不渝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}till death us do part.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.67,0:38:19.80,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我 克莱尔 伊丽莎白 毕彻姆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I, Claire Elizabeth Beauchamp
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.84,0:38:21.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,愿意嫁给\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}take, thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.64,0:38:26.18,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 亚历山大 马尔科姆 麦肯齐 弗雷泽\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}James Alexander Malcolm Mackenzie Fraser
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.48,0:38:29.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,作为我的丈夫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to be my wedded husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.23,0:38:33.68,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,从今开始 执子之手 与子偕老\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To have and to hold from this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.77,0:38:37.35,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,生死相依\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in sickness and in health...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.41,0:38:40.07,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,至死不渝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}till death us do part.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.91,0:38:43.33,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,准备好戒指了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you have the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.36,0:38:44.66,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.88,0:39:03.68,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.63,0:39:37.58,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,跟着我说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Say the words after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.25,0:39:45.81,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这些话到底啥意思\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What exactly did the words mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.89,0:39:48.81,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我们自此骨肉相连\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"You are blood of my blood and bone of my bone."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.90,0:39:55.60,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我奉献我的生命 我们合而为一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I give you my body that we two may be one."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.85,0:40:01.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我奉献我的灵魂\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I give you my spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.58,0:40:09.58,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,直到生命的尽头\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"Till our life shall be done."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.61,0:40:10.91,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,现在你可以吻你的新娘了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You may kiss yer bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.35,0:40:42.88,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,当时你吻我的样子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}When you kissed me like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.56,0:40:46.65,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,看来 你应该并不遗憾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}well, maybe you weren't so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.70,0:40:49.65,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,嫁给我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to be marrying me after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.85,0:41:08.11,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,把衣服脱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take off your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.19,0:41:11.28,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我想看看你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I want to look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.33,0:42:26.67,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,好吧那么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.55,0:42:29.75,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,要公平才行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}fair is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.72,0:42:34.09,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,也请你把衣服脱了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take off yours as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.61,0:43:00.50,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你过去从没见过裸体的女人吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Have you never seen a naked woman before?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.58,0:43:04.50,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,见过 不过从没这么靠近看过\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aye, but not one so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.00,0:43:13.86,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,而且没有看过属于我的身体\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And not one that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.40,0:43:34.23,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.51,0:43:59.51,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.59,0:44:00.51,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.59,0:44:02.60,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我不是故意弄疼你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didna mean to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.48,0:44:08.69,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你没有弄疼我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.74,0:44:09.69,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你确定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.69,0:44:14.69,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 哈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Yes. - Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.74,0:44:19.58,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道女人还会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I dinna know women could...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.50,0:44:23.54,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,每次都会这样吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Does it happen every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.67,0:44:29.87,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,除非那个男人是位很棒的情人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Only if the man is a very good lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.93,0:44:38.77,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,可你那么娇弱 我不想弄疼你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But you're so small. I didna want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.27,0:44:49.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 你在做什么 - 别动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What are you doing? - Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.87,0:44:59.70,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 疼吗 - 有点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Does that hurt? - Little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.74,0:45:01.57,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,要我停下吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you want me to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.66,0:45:03.71,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.74,0:45:05.21,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.57,0:46:05.40,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.35,0:46:10.36,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我还以为我的心烧起来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}"I thought my heart was gonna burst."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.37,0:47:16.42,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,弗雷泽夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mrs. Fraser.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.26,0:47:25.35,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 你这么晚才回来 - 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You're out late. - Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.38,0:47:27.47,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我刚见完兰德尔上尉回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm just back from seeing Captain Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.55,0:47:29.77,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我和他分享了愉快的消息\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I shared with him the happy news
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.85,0:47:32.89,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,跟他说你不会再听从他的指示了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that you're no longer at his beck and call.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.97,0:47:34.52,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他说什么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.56,0:47:36.19,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他说你说的蠢话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That there are likely limits even to your tolerance
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.28,0:47:39.33,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,毫无底线\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}for foul language.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.56,0:47:40.98,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得他应该不会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't suppose he means
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.07,0:47:42.62,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,采取进一步行动吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to take any further steps about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.70,0:47:43.90,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得不会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I shouldn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.98,0:47:45.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他还有比跟一个放荡英格兰女人纠缠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's got more important things to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.82,0:47:48.12,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,更重要的事儿要忙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}than chasing after one stray Sassenach,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.21,0:47:50.74,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不论她有多漂亮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}no matter how pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.79,0:47:52.29,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,他还不会至于绑架科勒姆侄子的老婆\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And he's got better sense than to rile Colum
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.38,0:47:53.91,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,来激怒他\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}by kidnapping his nephew's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.91,0:47:58.58,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,那我可以舒口气了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's comforting to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.63,0:48:01.17,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我很赞许你做了本分的事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I commend you for doing your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.06,0:48:08.72,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不过这些也不妨碍你去找点别的乐子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But it needn't stop you from sampling other pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.06,0:48:13.76,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,你是我见过最非凡的女人 克莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I find you to be the most singular woman, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.73,0:48:19.65,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我是杰米的妻子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm Jamie's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.03,0:48:34.73,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,晚上好 夫人 杜戈尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Evening, mistress, Dougal.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.82,0:48:36.65,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,晚上好 鲁伯特\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good evening, Rupert.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.96,0:48:43.59,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我想谢谢你的好意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I would like to thank you for your kindness towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.63,0:48:45.96,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,戒指很漂亮\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The... the ring is magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.05,0:48:48.80,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,哦 好吧 不用客气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh, well, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.85,0:48:51.10,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,由衷祝贺你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And a most hearty congratulations to you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.14,0:48:53.39,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,新婚快乐\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}on your wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.77,0:48:56.89,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.06,0:49:01.81,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,啊 小杰米可能没有什么经验\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah, young Jamie may no have much experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.86,0:49:04.53,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,不过这个女人看起来被管教得很好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but that one looks like well ridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.82,0:49:08.15,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这又是为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What was that fer?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.20,0:49:11.04,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,- 检查一下马匹 - 我检查过了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Check the horses. - I've already done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.12,0:49:13.54,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,再去检查一遍\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.52,0:50:17.55,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这是苏格兰珍珠\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're Scotch pearls.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.89,0:50:23.98,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我母亲的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They belonged to my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.06,0:50:26.56,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,现在属于我的妻子了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And now they belong to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.24,0:50:37.21,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,这是她留给我的仅存的几样东西之一\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're one of the few things I have left of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.24,0:50:41.21,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,对我来说弥足珍贵\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And very precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.92,0:50:47.30,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,就像你一样 克莱尔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}As are you, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.18,0:52:24.85,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,我们楼下见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll meet you downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.93,0:52:26.85,ssk 中文,,0,0,0,,如果我再不吃点东西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If I don't get something to eat soon,
